data.message: Fix Duro Dashboard incidents API - data extraction and route ordering: Fixed incidents.py router to extract RCA fields from nested content.data structure instead of content directly. Reordered routes so /incidents/stats/summary and /incidents/patterns come before /incidents/{incident_id}. Committed and pushed to origin/master.
data.task: Fix Duro Dashboard incidents API - data extraction and route ordering
data.outcome: Fixed incidents.py router to extract RCA fields from nested content.data structure instead of content directly. Reordered routes so /incidents/stats/summary and /incidents/patterns come before /incidents/{incident_id}. Committed and pushed to origin/master.
